OL,3,CBanned for life: Parliament decides
OL,4,Ccurrent under-18s will never legally
OL,5,Csmoke
OL,7,FChildren aged 17 or younger in the UK
OL,8,Fwill face a lifelong ban on buying
OL,9,Fcigarettes, as Parliament agrees on
OL,10,Fthe Tobacco and Vapes Bill.
OL,12,FBoth the Commons and Lords have
OL,13,Fsettled on a final draft of the
OL,14,Flegislation, which is designed to stop
OL,15,Fpeople who were born on or after
OL,16,FJanuary 1 2009 from ever taking up
OL,17,Fsmoking.
OL,19,FIt prohibits the sale of tobacco
OL,20,Fproducts to those born after 2008.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
