OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776812585
OL,3,CBanned for life: Parliament decides
OL,4,Ccurrent under-18s will never legally
OL,5,Csmoke
OL,7,FThe bill now awaits royal assent, the
OL,8,Ffinal stage of rule making that will
OL,9,Fformally make the bill into law. A
OL,10,Fdate for royal assent has not yet been
OL,11,Fset.
OL,13,FWhen the bill receives royal assent,
OL,14,Fministers will also get new powers to
OL,15,Fregulate tobacco, vaping and nicotine
OL,16,Fproducts, including their flavours and
OL,17,Fpackaging.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
