PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776812585
OL,3,CBanned for life: Parliament decides
OL,4,Ccurrent under-18s will never legally
OL,5,Csmoke
OL,7,F"It is a landmark Bill, it will create
OL,8,Fa smoke-free generation," Health
OL,9,Fminister Baroness Merron told the
OL,10,FLords on Monday.
OL,12,F"It is, in fact, the biggest public
OL,13,Fhealth intervention in a generation
OL,14,Fand I can assure all noble Lords it
OL,15,Fwill save lives."
OL,17,FLord Naseby, a Conservative former MP,
OL,18,Fsaid the Tobacco and Vapes Bill "does
OL,19,Fupset a great many people in that
OL,20,Findustry", including retailers.
