OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1776812585
OL,3,CBanned for life: Parliament decides
OL,4,Ccurrent under-18s will never legally
OL,5,Csmoke
OL,7,F"What we really need is a proper
OL,8,Funderstanding of how we educate people
OL,9,Fnot to take up smoking," he added.
OL,11,FIn response, Lady Merron said: "I can
OL,12,Foverall assure Lord Naseby, as I've
OL,13,Fdone on a number of occasions, about
OL,14,Fhow closely we have worked with
OL,15,Fretailers, and we will continue to do
OL,16,Fso."
